{
  "text": "Now the apparent Young's modulus needs to be converted to the Young's modulus of the rubber material. In the literature, [CITATION_1] to [CITATION_2] , several equations were used. By transforming the Gent and Lindley [CITATION_3] , Eq. (1), frequency-dependent Young's modulus of the rubber material is derived:",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "137661998",
    "[CITATION_2]": "122805131",
